Package org.ginsim.gui.utils.data

Class ObjectEditor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ginsim.gui.utils.data.ObjectEditor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - gui editor
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    GUIEditor<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RegulatoryGraphEditor, RegulatoryNodeEditor, StyleEditor
    public abstract class ObjectEditor<T>
extends Object
implements GUIEditor<T>
    An ObjectEditor acts as proxy between an object and the UI to edit its properties. It knows the available properties, can check if a proposed value is correct and can apply them.
